snippet.title: FIRST TIME IN PARIS (Paris vlog)
snippet.description:
My first time to travel in the City of Love, Paris! It was pretty gloomy on the days I was there but that did not stop me from touring around the beautiful city! Eiffel tower, Arc de Triomphe, Louvre Museum, Moulin Rouge, tried the famous Macaroons and even get to party despite how tired we were! In this video you'll know how expensive in Paris is, where to eat and what to do in Paris. Hope you guys enjoy this video as much I enjoyed my trip! Would appreciate if you can comment below your fave part of this vlog!

Comment, like, and subscribe!

INSTAGRAM: https://www.instagram.com/avelovin/
TWITTER: https://twitter.com/avelovinit

Stephanie's Instagram: @stephanie.bex

Tip: if u want to go to quite few museums in Paris, worth to get a Museum Pass :) if ure staying more than 3 days in Paris, u can buy the Paris Pass which includes 3 day train pass within zones 1-3, 2 day museum pass

When going anywhere in Europe worth to check SAndeman tours. They offer free walking tours all over Europe. Perfect to give you more idea of the place:)
